00:27:20,000 --> 00:27:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] on dođe koz njega i počne oni meditirati.

425
00:27:24,000 --> 00:27:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] I oni sad meditiraju 3 sata,

426
00:27:28,000 --> 00:27:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] onda sam pogledao 3 sata,

427
00:27:30,000 --> 00:27:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] šutio ništa.

