[SPEAKER_01] pa život je rijeka.

442
00:27:51,000 --> 00:27:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sam nastavio,

443
00:27:53,000 --> 00:27:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] dva sata prođeta,

444
00:27:55,000 --> 00:27:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] i žlava na kura budu.

445
00:27:58,000 --> 00:27:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Uff!

446
00:27:59,000 --> 00:28:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ja mislim o život trijeka.

447
00:28:01,000 --> 00:28:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro mi bitno,

448
00:28:15,000 --> 00:28:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] mi bitno.

449
00:28:16,000 --> 00:28:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, vidujte,

450
00:28:21,000 --> 00:28:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] da sam djec?

451
00:28:23,000 --> 00:28:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] nekih djekovita.

452
00:28:25,000 --> 00:28:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, dobro, dobro.

453
00:28:33,000 --> 00:28:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, ostavim savraniš,

454
00:28:34,000 --> 00:28:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] hvala.

455
00:28:35,000 --> 00:28:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sve što sam htio već,

456
00:28:38,000 --> 00:28:39,000
