00:28:42,000 --> 00:28:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] nije da ih sarce ruka može.

461
00:28:43,000 --> 00:28:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vidite, ja mislim bio nešto.

462
00:28:44,000 --> 00:28:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro.

463
00:28:48,000 --> 00:28:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad,

464
