[SPEAKER_01] vidimo da postoji tišina u praznini,

465
00:28:52,000 --> 00:28:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] i tišina u prisutnosti.

466
00:28:55,000 --> 00:28:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] I nije ta života u prisutnosti Boga.

467
00:28:57,000 --> 00:29:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sve to pismo nas uči,

468
00:29:00,000 --> 00:29:01,000
